487
00:33:29,466 --> 00:33:30,759
Maaf...

488
00:33:36,264 --> 00:33:37,474
Ujian tengah semester.

489
00:33:37,933 --> 00:33:39,976
UTS akan digantikan dengan tugas kelompok.

490
00:33:41,645 --> 00:33:44,189
